        <title>PREVENTIVE MAINTENANCE</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="pm" graphiccount="0">
            <title>AIR INDUCTION</title>
            <para>One of the single most important aspects of compressor preventive maintenance is the induction of
                clean air. The type and interval of maintenance required will vary depending upon the air induction
                system used.
            </para>
            <para>The intervals listed under the headings below pertain to typical highway and street operation. More
                frequent maintenance will be required for operation in dusty or dirty environments.
            </para>
        </svcproc>
